==爭議==
真鐸學校於2013年曾經爆出老師虐待及非禮學生事件，[[工黨_(香港)|工黨]]立法會議員[[張超雄|張超雄]]表示曾接收了30宗案件，當中21宗案件屬同一位老師，涉及暴力及色情。<ref name="Now20130517">{{cite web |title=張超雄：卅宗投訴真鐸學校老師暴力色情 |url=https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=68140 |accessdate=2020-04-04 |archive-date=2020-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502140554/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=68140 |dead-url=no }}</ref>事件其後獲教育局及警方跟進。<ref name="Now20130517-02">{{cite web |title=真鐸學生被非禮投訴已轉交警方 |url=https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=68149 |accessdate=2020-04-04 |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209210256/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=68149 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

